text: Abdelrahman Sameh (born 9 March 2000) is an Egyptian swimmer. He competed in the men's 50 metre butterfly at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian male swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Swimmers at the 2018 Summer Youth Olympics Category:Male butterfly swimmers
